OL,3,CBank of England holds interest rates
OL,4,Cbut warns more inflation yet to come
OL,6,FWords by Senior Business and Economics
OL,7,FProducer Jack Abbey
OL,9,FThe Bank of England has held interest
OL,10,Frates at 3.75% amid continuing
OL,11,Feconomic uncertainty caused by the
OL,12,Fvolatile situation in the Middle East.
OL,14,FIt appears that the Bank's worst fears
OL,15,Ffor the economic impact of the war may
OL,16,Fnot come to pass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
