FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781808494
OL,3,CBank of England holds interest rates
OL,4,Cbut warns more inflation yet to come
OL,6,FSince March, the closure of the Strait
OL,7,Fof Hormuz has provoked fears of a
OL,8,Fdevastating economic global shock as
OL,9,Foil and shipping remained unable to
OL,10,Fleave the Gulf.
OL,12,FSince talk of a peace deal began
OL,13,Fglobal energy prices have dropped
OL,14,Fsharply from the highs they reached
OL,15,Fduring the early days of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781808494
OL,3,CBank of England holds interest rates
OL,4,Cbut warns more inflation yet to come
OL,6,FWhen the Bank made its decision oil
OL,7,Fprices had fallen to $79 a barrel down
OL,8,Ffrom $100 last time they met. But that
OL,9,Fis still well above the $66 a barrel
OL,10,Fcost of oil before Donald Trump
OL,11,Flaunched his war against Iran.
OL,13,FThe situation in the Middle East
OL,14,Fthough remains far from certain and
OL,15,Fenergy prices across the board are
OL,16,Fvolatile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
