CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781808494
OL,3,CBank of England holds interest rates
OL,4,Cbut warns more inflation yet to come
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe job of the Bank's independent
OL,12,Fcommittee to ensure inflation hits its
OL,13,Ftarget of 2%. When inflation, or the
OL,14,Frisk of inflation is high they tend to
OL,15,Fincrease interest rates to try and
OL,16,Frein in spending and bring price rises
OL,17,Fdown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781808494
OL,3,CBank of England holds interest rates
OL,4,Cbut warns more inflation yet to come
OL,6,FAfter the high levels of inflation
OL,7,Fseen in the wake of Russia's invasion
OL,8,Fof Ukraine the Bank is extremely wary
OL,9,Fof what it calls second round effects
OL,10,Fof price rises where high prices lead
OL,11,Fto demands for wage increases which in
OL,12,Fturn lead to further price rises.
OL,14,FBefore the war began the Bank seemed
OL,15,Fset to slowly reduce interest rates
OL,16,Facross 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
