PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781808494
OL,3,CBank of England holds interest rates
OL,4,Cbut warns more inflation yet to come
OL,6,FThe war put a halt to that but a peace
OL,7,Fdeal and the possible reopening of the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz have reduced the
OL,9,Fchances of rate increases, news which
OL,10,Fwill relieve mortgage holders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
